UseAmmo (script event)
======================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Removes the specified amount of ammo from the player's inventory.

Usage
-----

*void* useAmmo( *value*' )

Parameters
----------

-   [value] - The amount of ammo to consume.

Examples
--------

` `
<font color="#0000ff">`useAmmo`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font>` `<font color="#0000dd">`1`</font>` `<font color="#000000">`)`</font>`;`

Notes
-----

This script event does not return any values.


